    <note xml:id="foot.f2"><ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_8631.xml">Cesare Alessandro Bressa</ref> founded the Bressa prize. CD recorded the receipt of £418 18<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. under the heading ‘Bressa prize’ on 17 January 1880 (CD’s Account books–banking account (Down House MS)).</note>
    <note xml:id="foot.f3"><hi rend="italic">Insectivorous plants</hi> (1875), <hi rend="italic">Cross and self fertilisation</hi> (1876), <hi rend="italic">Forms of flowers</hi> (1877).</note>
    <note xml:id="foot.f4">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-12376A.xml">letter from Ercole Ricotti, 29 December 1879</ref>.</note>
    <note xml:id="foot.f5">Mais collegues (But colleagues): Lessona probably meant to write ’Mes collègues’ (My colleagues).</note>
</div>        
            
